00:28:32,330 --> 00:28:33,270
 Do Not Enter-POLICE LINE-Under Investigation 

332
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:38,320
 Another unfortunate incident occurred yesterday at a profit organization, Cheong Ah Arts School. 

333
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:42,400
  At the CAA Festival which is regarded as the most grand tradition of the school, 

334
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:44,670
  the female senior student who won the  grand prize 

