340
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:24,400
There is significant damage to her brain. It doesn't look good.

341
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:27,240
You should prepare yourselves for the worst.

342
00:29:29,450 --> 00:29:30,960
Yun Hui.

343
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:46,030
This won't do. I'll get you a hospital room, go lie down even for a moment.

344
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:48,470
I'm fine.

345
00:29:48,470 --> 00:29:51,840
I've got to find the person who did that to my daughter first.

346
00:29:53,030 --> 00:29:57,590
What did the police say? Have they not found any evidence at all?

347
00:29:57,590 --> 00:30:00,320
They're still investigating. But not yet.

348
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:03,250
The culprit had to be at the school.

349
00:30:03,250 --> 00:30:06,560
How is it that they can't find any evidence? That makes no sense.

350
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:11,950
It's strange that the fire alarm was falsely activated too.

351
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:15,490
I  can't trust the police now.

352
00:30:16,550 --> 00:30:18,900
I need to go to the school myself.

353
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:21,010
What are you going to do when you're in this condition?

354
00:30:21,010 --> 00:30:22,370
Let's trust the police and wait for now.

355
00:30:22,370 --> 00:30:24,970
I asked someone I know to put in a word to the police.

356
00:30:24,970 --> 00:30:26,610
They'll contact us as soon as they find evidence.

357
00:30:26,610 --> 00:30:29,370
I really can't trust anyone.

358
00:30:29,370 --> 00:30:31,200
I'll catch him myself.

359
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:35,340
Do you think I'll let the people alone who hurt my daughter like that?

360
00:30:42,490 --> 00:30:46,870
Yun Cheol, what am I going to do if Ro Na dies?

361
00:30:46,870 --> 00:30:49,010
What am I going to do if she dies?

362
00:30:49,010 --> 00:30:52,800
I feel like I'm going crazy. What do I do, Yun Cheol?

363
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:55,920
No, no. My Ro Na.

364
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:59,840
Please save my Ro Na, Yun Cheol. Please.

365
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:07,150
Yun Hui, Yun Hui.

366
00:31:07,150 --> 00:31:09,290
Yun Hui! Yun Hui, Yun Hui!

367
00:31:09,290 --> 00:31:10,970
What are you doing? Call Doctor Jeong!

368
00:31:10,970 --> 00:31:14,000
Bring a respirator!

369
00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:29,730
  Su Ryeon, don't take my Ro Na. 

