00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:06,030
Don't answer the calls from your  friends for the time being.

378
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:15,410
Keep in mind. You're going to forget everything in the past.

379
00:33:15,410 --> 00:33:18,060
When you wake up from your sleep, it'll all have gone out of you.

380
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:50,740
  Eun Byeol had it. 

381
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:55,560
  The evidence that you killed Eun Byeol's grandfather. 

382
00:33:55,560 --> 00:33:58,700
  Did you like my video present? 

383
00:33:58,700 --> 00:34:01,190
  Chairwoman, Cheon Seo Jin? 

384
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:03,460
  Which bastard is it? 

385
00:34:03,460 --> 00:34:07,920
  Don't hide like a coward and show yourself!  

386
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:10,960
  So did you forget about it? 

387
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:12,990
 I mean my grandfather's accident. 

388
00:34:12,990 --> 00:34:14,240
  What are you talking about? 

389
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:18,760
  I took the medicine because I missed my grandfather so much. 

390
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:21,650
 Explain to me in a way I can understand! 

391
00:35:09,210 --> 00:35:10,830
  Authorized Personnel Only 

392
00:35:21,580 --> 00:35:23,730
When did you get here?

393
00:35:23,730 --> 00:35:25,320
Today.

394
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:28,260
How is Ro Na?

395
00:35:29,790 --> 00:35:31,630
Is she still unconcious?

396
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:35,510
Cheon Seo Jin and Eun Byeol's movements are suspicious.

397
00:35:36,870 --> 00:35:39,180
Tell me everything you know.

398
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:46,940
I took this picture at 5 a.m. this morning.

399
00:35:47,910 --> 00:35:50,260
Where is she going that early in the morning?

400
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:53,110
With a bag in her hand.

401
00:35:53,110 --> 00:35:56,700
The stranger thing is, she didn't have anything when she came back.

402
00:35:56,700 --> 00:36:00,440
Furthermore, she came back with Cheon Seo Jin.

403
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,460
Then by chance...

404
00:36:05,570 --> 00:36:10,050
The trophy... I need to get that trophy back.

405
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:13,560
It will be the end when that gets discovered.

406
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:22,590
The police just finished their investigation at the crime scene.

407
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:23,780
Are you sure?

408
00:36:23,780 --> 00:36:26,750
Apparently, they came to a dead end in finding evidence since their initial investigation failed.

409
00:36:26,750 --> 00:36:30,110
They are withdrawing from the scene, leaving only a minimum number of officers.

410
00:36:58,550 --> 00:37:00,750
Cheon Seo Jin?

411
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:22,260
  Ha Eun Byeol 

412
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,280
Did you see that?

413
00:37:33,350 --> 00:37:35,710
Ms. Cheon.

414
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:40,920
What are you doing here?

415
00:37:41,570 --> 00:37:46,490
Well, what are  you  doing here at this hour?

416
00:37:47,050 --> 00:37:51,680
Were you looking for something in the dark classroom with the lights off?

417
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:55,070
I'll say. I smell somthing fishy here.

418
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:57,320
What were you ransacking in there, like a thief?

419
00:37:57,320 --> 00:38:00,420
What do you mean ransacking? Me?

420
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:05,500
What?

421
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:09,160
The locker behind you

422
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:12,970
seems like a perfect place to hide something.

423
00:38:14,530 --> 00:38:15,550
Move aside.

424
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:17,560
There you go.

425
00:38:17,560 --> 00:38:21,040
Hurry and open them. You start with the ones on the left.

426
00:38:21,040 --> 00:38:24,210
I'll break open the ones from the right.

427
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:40,340
Wait!

428
00:38:42,530 --> 00:38:45,570
I'll open Ha Eun Byeol's.

429
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:04,780
What the heck? There's nothing in here.

430
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:15,410
There's only a few  left.

431
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:36,920
It's here!

432
00:39:40,250 --> 00:39:42,170
Whose locker is it?

433
00:39:43,070 --> 00:39:47,480
Ju Seok Gyeong! I knew it.

434
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:53,480
Let's go grab this wrench.

435
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:55,910
Let's go. Hurry.

436
00:40:08,450 --> 00:40:10,700
What are you doing here?

437
00:40:19,790 --> 00:40:23,030
Let go! I said let go of me!

438
00:40:23,860 --> 00:40:26,050
Do you know who my dad is?

439
00:40:26,050 --> 00:40:27,920
I'm not going!

440
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:30,420
Dad, where are you? Seok Gyeong is...

441
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:33,010
Seok Gyeong is being dragged away!

442
00:40:34,270 --> 00:40:36,300
What happened to your hand?

443
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:38,990
I was in a rush opening the lockers.

444
00:40:38,990 --> 00:40:40,890
How did you know?

445
00:40:40,890 --> 00:40:45,180
Eun Byeol called me.

446
00:40:45,180 --> 00:40:47,420
Were you the one who rang the fire alarm?

447
00:40:47,420 --> 00:40:49,090
No.

448
00:40:50,010 --> 00:40:52,490
I couldn't even imagine then.

449
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:58,570
Is it really Eun Byeol?

450
00:40:58,570 --> 00:41:02,340
Did our Eun Byeol really do that to Ro Na?

451
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:05,780
She didn't, right?

452
00:41:05,780 --> 00:41:07,890
I don't want to believe it either.

453
00:41:07,890 --> 00:41:10,820
Why didn't you tell me sooner? You should've told me first!

454
00:41:10,820 --> 00:41:12,950
How could I?

455
00:41:12,950 --> 00:41:17,020
You're Oh Yun Hui's husband now.

456
00:41:21,740 --> 00:41:24,670
I can't believe it. How could she?

457
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:27,640
How could my Eun Byeol do something like that?

458
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:30,180
It's already happened.

459
00:41:30,180 --> 00:41:32,690
Even if you don't want to believe it, you have to accept it.

460
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:36,240
No, no way.

461
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:38,550
This can't be happening.

462
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:41,880
You were the one who put the trophy in Seok Gyeong's locker.

463
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:45,580
That means you don't want Eun Byeol to be arrested either.

464
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:49,050
As her dad, all you did was disappoint her all the time.

465
00:41:49,050 --> 00:41:52,940
Will you just watch as your daughter's life is getting ruined?

466
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:55,770
They'll find out Seok Gyeong isn't the true culprit soon enough!

467
00:41:55,770 --> 00:41:58,250
So get it together!

468
00:41:58,250 --> 00:42:01,760
Yun Hui is never going to give up.

469
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:05,220
She's going to keep searching until she finds the real culprit.

470
00:42:05,850 --> 00:42:10,250
In the end, she's going to find out it's Eun Byeol.

471
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:14,040
When that happenes, our child's life is over.

472
00:42:17,010 --> 00:42:21,800
Save her. The only person who can save our Eun Byeol

473
00:42:22,670 --> 00:42:24,640
is you.

474
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:31,760
Eun Byeol's dad, please.

475
00:42:39,780 --> 00:42:42,590
What do you want me to do?

476
00:42:42,590 --> 00:42:44,690
I can't do it anymore.

477
00:42:44,690 --> 00:42:47,210
I feel sorry for Yun Hui.

478
00:42:47,210 --> 00:42:49,940
Seeing Ro Na  in the hospital bed like that is driving me crazy!

479
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:54,510
I heard there's no hope for Ro Na anyway.

480
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:57,090
I heard it from Doctor Jeong.

481
00:42:57,090 --> 00:42:59,980
That they'll declare her brain dead tomorrow.

482
00:42:59,980 --> 00:43:04,140
If that's the case, shouldn't the living go on living?

483
00:43:04,140 --> 00:43:07,670
What are you trying to say now?

484
00:43:07,680 --> 00:43:11,030
There's only one way to make Yun Hui give up.

485
00:43:11,030 --> 00:43:15,880
Making someone else the culprit while Seok Gyeong is buying time for us.

486
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,570
Cheon Seo Jin!

487
00:43:17,570 --> 00:43:19,860
For me, right now,

488
00:43:19,860 --> 00:43:21,830
Eun Byeol is the only thing I can see.

489
00:43:21,830 --> 00:43:26,090
I'm only going to think about Eun Byeol. I'm her mom.

490
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:30,930
And a mom has the responsibility of protecting her child.

491
00:43:30,930 --> 00:43:35,970
If something goes wrong with Eun Byeol, my life is over, too.

492
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:43,570
Damn it!

493
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:59,580
Why did you do that to my Ro Na?

494
00:43:59,580 --> 00:44:01,680
Did you hate Ro Na that much?

495
00:44:01,680 --> 00:44:07,100
Just hate me then! Why did you do that to Ro Na when she is innocent?! Why?! Why?!

496
00:44:07,100 --> 00:44:09,070
Ajumma, are you crazy?

497
00:44:09,070 --> 00:44:11,380
Why would I do such a thing?

498
00:44:11,380 --> 00:44:13,610
- Why did you do that? 
 - What do you think you're doing?

499
00:44:13,610 --> 00:44:15,790
Who are you to accuse my daughter of a crime?

500
00:44:15,790 --> 00:44:17,480
You stay out of this.

501
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:20,340
Seok Gyeong tried to kill Ro Na.

502
00:44:20,340 --> 00:44:24,300
A trophy with blood on it was found in Student Ju Seok Gyeong's locker.

503
00:44:24,300 --> 00:44:28,670
It can be presumed to be the instrument of this crime, so investigating your daughter was inevitable.

504
00:44:28,670 --> 00:44:30,590
A trophy?

505
00:44:30,590 --> 00:44:36,590
We heard your recent relationship with Bae Ro Na wasn't good, because of the incidents of school violence.

506
00:44:36,590 --> 00:44:41,410
You threw paint on her and even locked her in the bathroom.

507
00:44:42,130 --> 00:44:45,040
- About that— 
 - That incident is completely different from this.

508
00:44:45,040 --> 00:44:48,440
Seok Gyeong really isn't  the culprit. I can prove it.

